Detlef Horst Müller (born 13 June 1954 in Dissen, Lower Saxony)[1] is a German mathematician, specializing in analysis.[2]/nMüller received 1981 his doctorate from the University of Bielefeld with thesis Das Syntheseverhalten glatter Hyperflächen mit homogenen Krümmungsverhältnissen im 





R


n




